message: A number of commenters have asked if OWU accepts public funding. The answer is no, it does not. This does not mean that students do not recieve federal student aid. The Supreme Court ruled, in the mid 1980's, that Federal Student Aid does not constitute federal support of religious universities, and that students can use their student aid at any accredited school to pursue any degree they choose. OWU is consistently ranked as a top academic universtiy in America.
